# FocusFlow React Patterns

## State Management
- Local state: useState/useReducer
- Server state: React Query 5.0
- Global state: Zustand 4.5
- URL state: nuqs

## Component Guidelines
- Use Radix UI primitives with custom TailwindCSS styling
- Design tokens from `apps/web/styles/tokens.ts`
- Error boundaries: `apps/web/components/ErrorBoundary.tsx`
- Server actions for mutations: `apps/web/app/actions/`

## Performance
- Lazy load dashboard charts
- Use react-window for long lists
- Optimistic updates for timer operations
- Route-based code splitting

## Auth Pattern
Follow `apps/web/middleware.ts` for authentication.
All pages except `/auth/*` require authentication.

## Good Examples
- `apps/web/app/dashboard/components/TimerCard.tsx`
- `apps/web/lib/hooks/use-timer.ts`
- `services/api/src/services/ai/insights-generator.ts`
